data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home, boasting a cozy fireplace that adds warmth and character to the living space. The kitchen is the heart of this remarkable home. It includes an oversized island and offers an abundance of space for meal preparation, casual dining, and socializing as it is open to the living space. Fully finished Terrace level provides more living space, including a bedroom and has access to the backyard of the home. Primary bedroom and ensuite offer a relaxing space to retreat at the end of the day. Secondary bedrooms are ample sized and share the other full bath on the upper level. Deck off the Kitchen is a great spot to grill and relax. The location is ideal as it is minutes from downtown Smyrna and the Silver Comet trail.
